{
  "stem": "19895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And her husband was a very successful industrialist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in some degree, when I finished high school and I entered a mechanic training in a, in a company which was the telephone manufacturing company-- but telephone was just a name.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had many other aspects of the manufacturing business, such as railroad station signaling systems, and, and movie projectors, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I thought that someday I might be an industrialist myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this-- these were childish idealist visions of hope and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those changed during the years to follow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he-- his name was John Polachek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even so, if I never met him really-- yes, I did meet him, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a young boy when they visited in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I know I met him, although I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father and mother were observing Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a step more than that-- my father was an Orthodox Jew, but an enlightened Orthodox Jew, if I could categorize it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His appearance was very assimilated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't wear typical garb which was-- some of the country and, and religious Jews were known for and overemphasized.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because all the anti-Semitic cartoons and papers, they always showed Jews who looked totally different and dressed totally different, heavily bearded and sideburns hanging, the pious curling, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they always showed them in a very ugly scene.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and my family was very different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Looking in the back to Father's religious beliefs, he was an Orthodox man, a God-fearing man, who requested and we kept kosher home at home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even so, if after World War II when I returned from concentration camp and I grew up, I kind of had questions about the importance of that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I always observed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
